Rattrap, Ba, Rhinox SilverBolt and Primal  arrive at the mess hall and notice wolfblade
 
Rattrap :"hey wolfblade

Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@...> wrote:
WOlfblade::

"Alright. And drinks are on me if you win. Deal?"
She looked at Malice and winked at him. THen gave him a loving smile.
If he knew her, he would know she was up to something. 


--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, robert riley <bustercross365@y...> wrote:
> Malice/ Hellplague:
>  
> Malice took the offered darts and waited for a response from Celeron. 
>  
> Hellplague looked at her companion and sighed a bit.
>  
> "Go ahead, you could use some fun.  You might enjoy it."
> 
> Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@y...> wrote:
> Wolfblade:
> 
> She looked over at Celeron. "Hey, cheer up. Have a glass and relax.
> Don't look so down."
> She reached under the bar and grabbed three sets of darts. She tossed
> one set to Celeron and offered one set to Malice. "COme on, who's up
> for a game of Darts?"
> 
> 
> "HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill! 
Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!" 
>
